headline: CELEBRITY CRUISES' BUCKET LIST GALAPAGOS EXPEDITIONS ARE NOW OPEN FOR BOOKING IN 2027
summary: Celebrity Cruises' award-winning Galapagos expeditions on Celebrity Flora are now available for booking in 2027. Each 7-night, 10-night, 11-night or 16-night all-inclusive itinerary offers guests an unforgettable vacation experience while providing an opportunity to contribute to conservation efforts by taking part in reforestation in the region.
